data.description: "This home qualifies for a grant up to $17,500.  Ask me how." WELCOME HOME to this meticulously maintained home. This home boasts gorgeous hardwood floors throughout the first floor,  an updated kitchen, living room with a separate dining room space. Master bedroom, has a huge walk in closet, and lots of natural light. The additional bedroom is located on the first floor along with a full bathroom. From the kitchen go down to the basement where the seller has turned the space into a she cave. The backyard is untouched waiting on you to turn it into an oasis that will be perfect for entertaining. This home is located on a one way street that is close to downtown, transportation and all major highways.
